cus collapsed rbs ended up on the hook for most of the losses subscription required  sec charges goldman sachs with fraud in structuring and marketing of cdo tied to subprime mortgages press release us securities and exchange commission april     a b c goldman sachs makes further comments on sec complaint press release business wire april     corkery michael april   goldman responds again to sec complaint the wall street journal subscription required  salmon felix april   goldmans misleading statement on aca reuters   maguire tom april   cnbc on the goldman complaint  this is surreal justoneminutetypepadcom   pitt harvey april   the secs dangerous gamble the daily beast   goldman in the eye of the beholder the atlantic october     jones ashby april   goldman v sec its all about materiality the wall street journal subscription required  federal crisis inquiry report p  fiderer david may   the moral compass missing from the greatest trade ever the huffington post   zuckerman gregory april   inside paulsons deal with goldman daily beast retrieved february   scott eichel a senior bear stearns trader was among those at the investment bank who sat through a meeting with paulson but later turned down the idea he worried that paulson would want especially ugly mortgages for the cdos like a bettor asking a football owner to bench a star quarterback to improve the odds of his wager against the team either way he felt it would look improper  it didnt pass the ethics standards it was a reputation issue and it didnt pass our moral compass   bethany mclean joe nocera all the devils are here the hidden history of the financial crisis p   in truth the legal issues were far from the most disturbing thing about abacus aci   a b the goldman case legal or illegal the abacus deal was morally wrong wall street needs a new compass houston chronicle april     called abacus   a b mclean and nocera all the devils are here  p  raymond nate august   sec wins as exgoldman executive tourre found